<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-C%C6%A1-T%C3%BAc/author-aRixw0HrQAwmg0YXhGmskA">Bùi Cơ Túc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/T%C3%AD-D%E1%BA%A1-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-6zYzZx8bQhzm8Wdeftq7Wg">Tí Dạ ca kỳ 1 - 子夜歌其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-x2jHtUhu4KZY4kl0A-lAIw">Lý Dục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Mai-Pha/Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-mai-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-zSPC6PVp1fcZemvavfPMhQ">Tuyết mai kỳ 1 - 雪梅其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Mai-Pha/author-RsrtOLmUMIuICsXh29zWQw">Lư Mai Pha</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%C3%BAc/poem-HuigctC5XcbeFCZOHbQCSw">Vịnh cúc - 詠菊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/X%C3%ADch-Gi%C3%A1p/poem-w6Fg1ZbIHIRI4CYERIRbPA">Xích Giáp - 赤甲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
